{"tid":282000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人點解咁鍾意俾氣人受","createTime":"2017-06-13T04:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T05:03:04.000Z","uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"019ac14df84d0795740191846abb0444d3cb1dd2","tid":282000,"uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"先利申我三代都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解宜家啲人咁鍾意俾氣人受<br />\n返工又要受老屎忽、老世氣<br />\n但點解連出街消費都要受氣？<br />\n我去剪個頭髮又好 <br />\n去配眼鏡又好<br />\n連去食個飯都好<br />\n啲人都西口西面 有時仲會串串貢<br />\n反而我返工嗰度無受過客人氣<br />\n啲客全部好有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明十年前香港都唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好掛住以前嘅香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccccf5a46d83d4749a6c68841838276fb860e200","tid":282000,"uid":22743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"都冇值得開心既事 點會唔西面"},{"pid":"76fd2eaed8671853d1a74dc822c82026ea6be5c0","tid":282000,"uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都冇值得開心既事 點會唔西面</blockquote><br />\n咁都唔駛無啦啦俾氣人受掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}